videos.description: Arizona State grabs two straight offensive rebounds which lead to a Romello White turnaround jumper
videos.headline: ASU's White scores after offensive rebound

videos.description: Kodi Justice uses his body well and makes the left-handed layup to score.
videos.headline: ASU's Justice drives and makes tough layup

videos.description: Mickey Mitchell steals the pass and goes all the way to jam it home for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: ASU's Mitchell gets steal and dunks it home

videos.description: Tra Holder gets the steal and is able to blow by defenders to score a layup in transition.
videos.headline: ASU turns steal into Holder layup

videos.description: Tra Holder drains a 3-pointer to give Arizona State a 1-point lead at halftime over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Holder's 3-pointer at buzzer gives ASU lead

videos.description: Shannon Evans II shows off his nice handles to create space and hits a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: ASU's Evans uses nice crossover to drain 3-pointer

videos.description: Romello White blocks the layup attempt and runs the floor to jam it home for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: White's block leads to dunk on other end

videos.description: Archie Bradley is having some fun at the Arizona State game by showing off his wrestling moves and being a part of the Curtain of Distraction.
videos.headline: D-Backs pitcher Bradley stars in ASU's Curtain of Distraction

videos.description: Tra Holder forces a steal and makes the spectacular pass to Shannon Evans II who makes the up-and-under layup for Arizona State.
videos.headline: Holder's no-look pass leads Evan's layup
